You can set the default address with this command if you insert valid address after this word:

Examples:
---------------
<b>address:Paris
address:Roma
address:London</b>

The value after the address have to be available in the database.
The value of this setting is case sensitive and must be same as the content of address filed in the database.

Remove your personal address settings:
<b>address:reset</b>

Show all your current settings:
<b>setting:show</b>

Please use /help if you need more information.